|date=2009-03-13
|accessdate=2009-04-09}}</ref> the [[Asian American Journalists Association]],<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.aaja.org/news/Headliners/2009_03_04_01/
|title=AAJA Calls for Release of Journalist Detained in Iran
